    'community-garden-clean-up',
    'Community Garden Clean-Up',
    'With winter approaching, the PCA decided to help prepare for the coming spring by helping tidy up. Around 15 volunteers gathered at Herron Avenue Flower Garden, supporting the Western Pennsylvania Conservancy. The volunteers toiled in the pouring rain to help remove annual flowers and weeds. Than...',
    1,
    $content$[{"type":"paragraph","text":"With winter approaching, the PCA decided to help prepare for the coming spring by helping tidy up. Around 15 volunteers gathered at Herron Avenue Flower Garden, supporting the Western Pennsylvania Conservancy. The volunteers toiled in the pouring rain to help remove annual flowers and weeds. Thanks to all who came out and helped! We appreciate the continued effort to keep our community in great shape."}]$content$::jsonb,
