    'the-fall-mash-up',
    'Fall Mash-Up',
    'Fall has arrived! The PCA Youth Center celebrated the change of seasons with a Fall Mash Up event at Deer Browse Shelter 1 in North Park. Attendees participated in many different activities, such as a potato sack race and a scavenger hunt for candy. Best of all, the participants enjoyed painting...',
    1,
    $content$[{"type":"paragraph","text":"Fall has arrived! The PCA Youth Center celebrated the change of seasons with a Fall Mash Up event at Deer Browse Shelter 1 in North Park. Attendees participated in many different activities, such as a potato sack race and a scavenger hunt for candy. Best of all, the participants enjoyed painting pumpkins! Overall, the event was a blast! Thanks to all the volunteers who helped out and to all the contributors who supported our mission. Stay tuned for our next events!"}]$content$::jsonb,
