    'cultural-festival',
    'Cultural Festival',
    'To wrap up September, the PCA Youth participated in the Pittsburgh Chinese Cultural Festival held in Mellon Park. People who visited were able to browse the many booths that showcased Chinese culture through activities, food, and merchandise. The PCA Youth had our very own booth that allowed visi...',
    1,
    $content$[{"type":"paragraph","text":"To wrap up September, the PCA Youth participated in the Pittsburgh Chinese Cultural Festival held in Mellon Park. People who visited were able to browse the many booths that showcased Chinese culture through activities, food, and merchandise. The PCA Youth had our very own booth that allowed visitors to try out Chinese calligraphy or to purchase their own customizable bookmarks. We would like to thank all the volunteers who helped to run our booth and those who stopped by for supporting our mission. Make sure to keep an eye out for any of our future events!"}]$content$::jsonb,
