(
    'mckeesport-area-food-distribution',
    'McKeesport Area Food Distribution',
    'With summer coming to a close, the PCA Youth Center participated in one last event before school started, a food distribution event hosted by the Greater Pittsburgh Community Food Bank.',
    1,
    $content$[{"type":"paragraph","text":"With summer coming to a close, the PCA Youth Center participated in one last event before school started, a food distribution event hosted by the Greater Pittsburgh Community Food Bank."},{"type":"paragraph","text":"The distribution took place at McKeesport Area Highschool, where 25 of our own participants worked together under the hot sun to provide a variety of fresh produce and other foods to many families in need."},{"type":"paragraph","text":"In the end, the event was a great success. The PCA Youth and our volunteers are glad to have impacted many people in our community and hope to do so again in the future. Thanks again to all of the organizers and participants who allowed us to carry this event out."}]$content$::jsonb,
    'local',
